OL,3,C"It was like talking to a friend":
OL,4,CCouple lose thousands in holiday fraud
OL,6,FA couple from Hampshire have told how
OL,7,Fthey were conned out of thousands of
OL,8,Fpounds by an 'amenable' woman from
OL,9,FPortsmouth who was jailed for running
OL,10,Fa Ponzi-style holiday fraud.
OL,12,FJohn and Terry Ross from Hedge End
OL,13,Flost #15,000 after booking three
OL,14,Fholidays through Shelley Simpson, who
OL,15,Fwas sentenced to 33 months in jail on
OL,16,FWednesday (6 May).
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
