PN,41802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1778166668
OL,3,C"It was like talking to a friend":
OL,4,CCouple lose thousands in holiday fraud
OL,6,FSimpson, 46, of Westwood Road,
OL,7,FPortsmouth, ran Sphere Events Limited
OL,8,Fbetween March 2019 and November 2022,
OL,9,Ftaking people's money while pretending
OL,10,Fto make holiday and event bookings.
OL,12,FAnd Mr and Mrs Ross have described how
OL,13,FSimpson gained their trust during
OL,14,Ftheir interactions, even forcing them
OL,15,Fto pay by bank transfer by saying that
OL,16,Fher credit card machine was broken,
OL,17,Fmeaning they couldn't get their money
OL,18,Fback.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1778166668
OL,3,C"It was like talking to a friend":
OL,4,CCouple lose thousands in holiday fraud
OL,6,FThe Ross's added: "It's like a friend,
OL,7,Ftalking to a friend on the phone,
OL,8,Finterested in everything we did"
OL,10,F"She came over very amenable, didn't
OL,11,Fshe?"
OL,13,F"She said the credit card machine was
OL,14,Fbroken, basically if we'd used a
OL,15,Fcredit card, we'd have been able to
OL,16,Fclaim our money back."
OL,18,FPat and Christopher Moyeses were also
OL,19,Fimpacted by Simpson's holiday fraud.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1778166668
OL,3,C"It was like talking to a friend":
OL,4,CCouple lose thousands in holiday fraud
OL,6,FAlthough they got their money back,
OL,7,Fthey're still impacted by it.
OL,9,FMrs Moyes said: "I felt stupid, I felt
OL,10,Fsilly that I hadn't checked things.
OL,12,F"These days now we check everything
OL,13,Fbefore we pay any money out to
OL,14,Fanybody, make sure it's always on the
OL,15,Fcredit card or through the bank"
OL,17,F"I just feel her sentence was too
OL,18,Fshort, considering they say she could
OL,19,Fbe out well before Christmas."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
