CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1778166668
OL,3,C"It was like talking to a friend":
OL,4,CCouple lose thousands in holiday fraud
OL,6,FPortsmouth Trading Standards and
OL,7,FHampshire Police initially received
OL,8,Fmore than 90 complaints from consumers
OL,9,Fwho had paid for holidays or events
OL,10,Fbut either never received their
OL,11,Fbookings, were provided with falsified
OL,12,Fdocumentation, or were left paying
OL,13,Fsubstantial additional costs for
OL,14,Freplacement flights and accommodation.
OL,16,FThe court heard that Simpson relied on
OL,17,Fcustomers paying in full upfront for
OL,18,Fwhat they believed were discounted
OL,19,Fholidays.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
