OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1778166668
OL,3,C"It was like talking to a friend":
OL,4,CCouple lose thousands in holiday fraud
OL,6,FIn reality, these discounts did not
OL,7,Fexist, and payments taken from new
OL,8,Fcustomers were used to cover other
OL,9,Fdebts and her personal spending,
OL,10,Fincluding private school fees.
OL,12,FElectronic devices seized during the
OL,13,Ftrading standards investigation
OL,14,Frevealed a repeated pattern of
OL,15,Ffalsified booking confirmations and
OL,16,Ffinancial documents, including forged
OL,17,Fbank statements used to falsely claim
OL,18,Fpayments had been made to hotels,
OL,19,Fairlines and venues.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1778166668
OL,3,C"It was like talking to a friend":
OL,4,CCouple lose thousands in holiday fraud
OL,6,FIn some cases, families discovered
OL,7,Fwhile already on holiday that flights
OL,8,For accommodation had not been paid
OL,9,Ffor, forcing them to make lastminute
OL,10,Farrangements at substantial personal
OL,11,Fcost and, in effect, paying twice for
OL,12,Ftheir holiday.
OL,14,FOthers paid tens of thousands of
OL,15,Fpounds for luxury or
OL,16,Fonceinalifetime trips, including
OL,17,Fhoneymoons, which were never booked at
OL,18,Fall.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
