OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1778166668
OL,3,C"It was like talking to a friend":
OL,4,CCouple lose thousands in holiday fraud
OL,6,FOne customer paid #37,000 for a luxury
OL,7,Ffamily holiday to Barbados. Simpson
OL,8,Fnever made the booking and used the
OL,9,Fmoney to pay off business debts.
OL,11,FAnother couple paid for a honeymoon to
OL,12,Fthe Maldives which was never booked.
OL,14,FEvidence heard by the court
OL,15,Fhighlighted the scale of the harm
OL,16,Fcaused, with customers and businesses
OL,17,Fleft out of pocket and facing anxiety,
OL,18,Fdisruption and uncertainty as a result
OL,19,Fof Simpson's deception.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
