FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1778166668
OL,3,C"It was like talking to a friend":
OL,4,CCouple lose thousands in holiday fraud
OL,6,FPortsmouth Trading Standards team will
OL,7,Fnow pursue 'Proceeds of Crime Act'
OL,8,Fproceedings with a view to
OL,9,Fcompensating the many victims in this
OL,10,Fcase.
OL,12,FLord Michael Bichard, Chair of
OL,13,FNational Trading Standards, said:
OL,14,F"Simpson's actions took advantage of
OL,15,Fpeople who had saved hard for dream
OL,16,Fholidays, honeymoons and once-in-a-
OL,17,Flifetime trips. She left some victims
OL,18,Fstranded abroad, facing significant
OL,19,Femotional distress and, in some cases,
OL,20,Ftens of thousands of pounds out of
OL,21,Fpocket.
OL,26,@vD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/11
