OL,3,C"It was like talking to a friend":
OL,4,CCouple lose thousands in holiday fraud
OL,6,F"Fraud like this not only devastates
OL,7,Fholidaymakers, it also harms
OL,8,Flegitimate businesses who play by the
OL,9,Frules.
OL,11,FAs we approach the summer holiday
OL,12,Fseason, we urge people to be cautious
OL,13,Fof deals that seem too good to be
OL,14,Ftrue, to check independent reviews and
OL,15,Fto report any concerns to Citizens
OL,16,FAdvice consumer service on 0808 223
OL,17,F1133."
OL,26,@nD@AOUyD@FO]
